<h1 id='emrapi-configuration'>EMRAPI Configuration</h1><h2 id='emr-api-configuration-overview'>EMR API Configuration Overview</h2>
<p>The EMR API module provides several high-level APIs and configuration settings.  The configuration endpoint provided by the <code>emrapi</code> module enables RESTful access to these configuration values.</p>
<h2 id='available-operations-for-emrapi-configuration'>Available operations for EMRAPI Configuration</h2>
<ol>
<li><a href="#get-emrapi-configuration">Get EMRAPI Configuration</a></li>
</ol>
<h2 id='get-emrapi-configuration'>Get EMRAPI Configuration</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>Get EMRAPI configuration</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>GET /openmrs/ws/rest/v1/emrapi/configuration
</code></pre></div><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight java tab-java"><code>
